      </p>

      <p>
        Your player profile is used to store game progress, scores, achievements,
        preferences, and gameplay history. Authentication may include third-party
        sign-in providers such as Google Sign-In.
      </p>

      <div class="warning">
        <strong>Important:</strong> Deleting your account is permanent and cannot be undone.
      </div>

      <h3>When you delete your account:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>All game progress (levels, scores, records, and achievements) will be permanently deleted;</li>
        <li>All earned or purchased in-game items will be removed;</li>
        <li>All personal data, preferences, and usage history will be erased from our servers.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Delete Your Account from the App</h3>
      <div class="steps">
        <ol>
          <li>Open the <strong>Think Fast</strong> app;</li>
          <li>Go to the <strong>Profile</strong> page;</li>
          <li>Tap <strong>“Delete my account”</strong>;</li>
          <li>Read the information carefully and confirm your request.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <h3>Alternative Account and Data Deletion Method</h3>
